OL,7,FNatalie Needham's son Kouper died
OL,8,Funexpectedly at home in July 2019, at
OL,9,Fjust a day old.
OL,11,FAn inquest into his death found he had
OL,12,Fdied of respiratory distress.
OL,14,FNatalie made a Subject Access Request
OL,15,F(SAR) from Nottingham University
OL,16,FHospitals Trust in the years following
OL,17,FKouper's death as she believed there
OL,18,Fwere failings in his care.
