OL,7,FIn a serious data breach, Natalie from
OL,8,FHucknall was given files not only
OL,9,Fcontaining information about her son
OL,10,Fbut also sensitive information about
OL,11,Ffour other families.
OL,13,FShe said: "In going through them all
OL,14,Fwe came across other people's medical
OL,15,Frecords, which were quite intrusive
OL,16,Frecords and it's records that I
OL,17,Fwouldn't want disclosed to other
OL,18,Fpeople if it was about me. It wasn't
OL,19,Fjust a little bit of information, it
OL,20,Fwas quite detailed.
