OL,7,F"It affected me really badly."
OL,9,FAround 2,000 families are now part of
OL,10,FNottingham's ongoing Independent
OL,11,FMaternity Review, led by former senior
OL,12,Fmidwife Donna Ockenden.
OL,14,FNottingham University Hospitals Trust
OL,15,Fhas apologised for the mistakes made
OL,16,Fwith the SAR but Natalie said families
OL,17,Fmust feel confident their personal
OL,18,Finformation is safe.
