OL,7,FShe said: "There needs to be more than
OL,8,Fan apology, they need to show that
OL,9,Fchange is happening and it's not going
OL,10,Fto happen again that they've put the
OL,11,Fright tools in place to prevent it
OL,12,Ffrom happening."
OL,14,F"There's a lot of people now wanting
OL,15,Fmedical records, how many more
OL,16,Ffamilies is it going to happen to
OL,17,Fbecause we've got no evidence that
OL,18,Fit's not going to happen again."
