OL,7,FNatalie said something that should
OL,8,Fhave helped her made sense of her
OL,9,Fson's death has left her traumatised.
OL,11,FShe said: "That's all we have of our
OL,12,Fson, is his medical records, that's
OL,13,Fall we have left now and to know that
OL,14,Fthat could be potentially sent to
OL,15,Fother families.
OL,17,F"That's sensitive information and it's
OL,18,Fmy son's information and it shouldn't
OL,19,Fhappen."
