OL,7,FIn a statement, Anthony May, Chief
OL,8,FExecutive at Nottingham University
OL,9,FHospitals said: "I would like to
OL,10,Fapologise for mistakes we have made
OL,11,Fwith their Subject Access Requests
OL,12,F(SARs), it is totally unacceptable.
OL,14,F"We do have processes to ensure the
OL,15,Fquality of our SARs, but these fell
OL,16,Fshort of what we would expect in these
OL,17,Fcases. I have now commissioned an
OL,18,Furgent review of our Quality Assurance
OL,19,Fprocesses.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
