OL,7,F"I recognise the importance of timely
OL,8,Fand accurate responses to these
OL,9,Frequests for the families involved in
OL,10,Fthe Independent Maternity Review. I am
OL,11,Fcommitted to improving this area of
OL,12,Four work and while we have made some
OL,13,Fimprovements, there is more to do.
OL,15,F"So far, we have restructured the team
OL,16,Fand have 14 new colleagues joining us
OL,17,Fto help improve the timeliness of our
OL,18,Fresponses, balancing this against
OL,19,Fensuring quality and accuracy.
