OL,7,F"The process for requesting access to
OL,8,Fhealth records is also under review.
OL,10,F"More generally we are looking at ways
OL,11,Fto improve our support for families
OL,12,Faffected by the Independent Maternity
OL,13,FReview. I intend to bring some of this
OL,14,Fdetail to our Annual Public Meeting on
OL,15,F18 September."
